reviewText: This is yet another multi-pack of films from Mill Creek Entertainment.  If you have several of these, like I do, than you will have alot of overlap of movies.  But the Dead of Night collection is simply Mill Creek Entertainment's Midnight Madness 20 Movie Collection under a different name.  whichever name you buy this set under, You will get a great set of B-Rate Cheesy films!  And I do LOVE my cheese!
